1
00:01:13,519 --> 00:01:14,400
I'm going to pick up Yang Hui.

2
00:01:14,879 --> 00:01:15,599
Want to come along?

3
00:01:16,439 --> 00:01:17,560
You go ahead, I'll work out a bit more.

4
00:01:18,200 --> 00:01:18,719
Alright.

5
00:01:32,200 --> 00:01:33,599
Keep at it.

6
00:01:49,280 --> 00:01:51,000
President He, what a coincidence.

7
00:01:51,000 --> 00:01:52,280
You like working out too?

8
00:01:54,640 --> 00:01:55,640
And you are?

9
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:57,680
Important people are always so forgetful.

10
00:01:57,959 --> 00:01:59,680
I'm the sales director at Hejing Company.

11
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:01,159
We've met before.

12
00:02:01,560 --> 00:02:02,159
Oh.

13
00:02:02,439 --> 00:02:03,439
I don't really remember.

14
00:02:04,159 --> 00:02:05,400
Do you come here to work out often?

15
00:02:07,439 --> 00:02:08,919
What if I told you I came here

16
00:02:09,439 --> 00:02:10,479
just to find you?

17
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:14,439
Please don't joke like that.

18
00:02:14,919 --> 00:02:15,960
My kid's already in school.

19
00:02:18,719 --> 00:02:19,960
Do you think

20
00:02:21,080 --> 00:02:22,639
I'm not as pretty as your wife?

21
00:02:23,479 --> 00:02:24,319
Please have some self-respect.

22
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:28,199
President He.

23
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:30,560
Why keep me at arm's length?

24
00:02:30,919 --> 00:02:31,719
I came here

25
00:02:31,719 --> 00:02:33,159
just to learn some fitness tips from you.

26
00:02:34,479 --> 00:02:35,639
I'm not a gym trainer.

27
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:36,599
I can't teach you anything.

28
00:02:39,599 --> 00:02:41,000
Oh, what a blockhead.

29
00:02:58,240 --> 00:02:59,479
Hey, Bingbing.

30
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:02,120
That blockhead won't take the bait.

31
00:03:03,479 --> 00:03:04,120
I'm coming over.

32
00:03:13,639 --> 00:03:14,319
President He.

33
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:15,639
You're here too?

34
00:03:17,080 --> 00:03:17,759
What a coincidence.

35
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:22,599
President Fang.

36
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:23,840
Staging an encounter, huh?

37
00:03:24,919 --> 00:03:26,280
A little tea money.

38
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:27,639
Please accept it.

39
00:03:34,199 --> 00:03:34,759
Fang Bing.

40
00:03:35,319 --> 00:03:36,159
What are you doing?

41
00:03:36,960 --> 00:03:38,039
Bribing me openly?

42
00:03:38,960 --> 00:03:39,400
President He.

43
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:40,719
What are you getting so worked up about?

44
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:43,120
It's just tea money, my treat.

45
00:03:43,599 --> 00:03:44,520
Just a small gesture.

46
00:03:45,439 --> 00:03:46,719
Put your little trinkets away.

47
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:48,879
If Xiao Yifan hadn't allowed you

48
00:03:48,879 --> 00:03:49,879
to bid on the general contracting,

49
00:03:50,360 --> 00:03:51,520
you wouldn't even make it through

50
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:52,120
my company's doors.

51
00:03:52,840 --> 00:03:53,639
If you want to do business,

52
00:03:54,319 --> 00:03:55,400
put your cards on the table

53
00:03:55,919 --> 00:03:57,280
and compete with real strength.

54
00:03:59,039 --> 00:03:59,560
President He.

55
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:01,199
We're all old friends here.

56
00:04:01,199 --> 00:04:01,960
Is this really necessary?

57
00:04:03,039 --> 00:04:04,120
If this tea money isn't enough,

58
00:04:05,039 --> 00:04:07,080
I'll add more once the deal's done.

59
00:04:08,319 --> 00:04:09,199
Once the deal's done?

60
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:10,560
What deal?

61
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:12,039
Fang Bing.

62
00:04:13,039 --> 00:04:14,319
You're trying to frame me.

63
00:04:14,919 --> 00:04:15,479
And another thing.

64
00:04:16,079 --> 00:04:17,680
Are you working with Li Yao?

65
00:04:18,079 --> 00:04:19,319
Are you rigging the bids?

66
00:04:21,879 --> 00:04:23,120
If I find out you are,

67
00:04:24,079 --> 00:04:25,560
you'll never win a bid in your life.

68
00:04:29,399 --> 00:04:29,959
President He.

69
00:04:31,759 --> 00:04:33,720
I sincerely want to be your friend.

70
00:04:35,079 --> 00:04:36,519
Do you have to be so cold?

71
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:38,319
Fang Bing.

72
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:40,360
Look at the entire industry.

73
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:41,879
Who else is as greedy as you?

74
00:04:42,879 --> 00:04:44,600
A man like you, my friend? Hardly.

75
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:46,480
Why don't you first learn

76
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:47,959
how to be an honest businessman.

77
00:04:48,839 --> 00:04:50,560
I'm well aware of the bid rigging.

78
00:04:51,279 --> 00:04:51,879
Tomorrow,

79
00:04:52,439 --> 00:04:53,439
I'll tell the whole truth,

80
00:04:53,639 --> 00:04:54,399
including how you bribed me,

81
00:04:54,839 --> 00:04:55,720
to President Zheng.

82
00:05:10,399 --> 00:05:11,199
He Junjie.

83
00:05:12,319 --> 00:05:14,040
If you dare expose my bid rigging,

84
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:16,759
I'll kill you.

85
00:05:29,399 --> 00:05:30,160
Bing.

86
00:05:31,439 --> 00:05:32,480
You were in a rush to see me.

87
00:05:32,639 --> 00:05:33,399
Just say the word.

88
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:35,279
He Junjie doesn't appreciate my favor.

89
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:36,560
Find a way to get rid of him.

90
00:05:37,720 --> 00:05:38,319
Bing.

91
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:39,600
Calm down.

92
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:41,959
We can still be friends without a deal.

93
00:05:42,319 --> 00:05:43,680
Let's not stir up trouble.

94
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:47,000
If not for my support all these years,

95
00:05:47,199 --> 00:05:48,639
would you have the life you do now?

96
00:05:59,319 --> 00:06:00,160
This money

97
00:06:00,720 --> 00:06:01,800
is enough for you to disappear.

98
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:06,560
Tomorrow, I'll make sure he can't set foot

99
00:06:06,560 --> 00:06:08,079
inside Wanhe Real Estate.

100
00:06:46,720 --> 00:06:47,199
What's wrong?

101
00:06:47,319 --> 00:06:48,199
Something on your mind?

102
00:06:54,240 --> 00:06:55,360
Today at the gym,

103
00:06:55,680 --> 00:06:57,360
Fang Bing tried to bribe me. I refused.

104
00:06:58,959 --> 00:07:00,439
These next few days, when you pick up the kids,

105
00:07:00,480 --> 00:07:01,040
be careful on the road.

106
00:07:01,879 --> 00:07:02,639
I'm afraid

107
00:07:02,639 --> 00:07:04,160
it's more than just bribery, isn't it?

108
00:07:04,240 --> 00:07:04,639
Tell me.

109
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:06,000
Was there anything else?

110
00:07:07,560 --> 00:07:08,319
Honey,

111
00:07:08,519 --> 00:07:09,319
don't you worry.

112
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:10,879
Back when I was chasing you,

113
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:12,079
I put in a lot of effort, you know.

114
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:16,439
At least you have a conscience.

115
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:17,519
A couple of days ago,

116
00:07:17,519 --> 00:07:19,079
Su Yuanyuan tried to slip me a gift too.

117
00:07:19,319 --> 00:07:20,000
I turned it down.

118
00:07:22,759 --> 00:07:24,519
Fang Bing is a vicious snake.

119
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:25,879
He's exploiting every loophole.

120
00:07:26,839 --> 00:07:27,800
It's impossible to guard against him.

121
00:07:29,199 --> 00:07:30,319
Let's not overthink it.

122
00:07:30,319 --> 00:07:31,079
Let's get some sleep first.

123
00:07:34,720 --> 00:07:35,519
Turn off the light.

124
00:07:42,519 --> 00:07:43,839
First, the gorgeous director

125
00:07:43,839 --> 00:07:45,199
throws herself at me.

126
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:47,800
Then Fang Bing offers tea money.

127
00:07:48,839 --> 00:07:50,639
Could it really be such a coincidence?

128
00:07:54,160 --> 00:07:55,000
To win

129
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:56,360
the general contracting for Plot 7,

130
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:57,600
Fang Bing even went after Li Yao.

131
00:07:58,480 --> 00:07:59,480
He's out for blood.

132
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:15,160
We're really on the same wavelength.

133
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:16,199
I was just about to call you.

134
00:08:19,959 --> 00:08:20,519
Really?

135
00:08:20,680 --> 00:08:21,439
What are you up to?

136
00:08:22,240 --> 00:08:23,120
Just finished my workout.

137
00:08:23,439 --> 00:08:24,360
Heading to the sales office soon.

138
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:25,319
Once I get to the office,

139
00:08:25,720 --> 00:08:26,160
Why?

140
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:27,000
Missing me?

141
00:08:28,120 --> 00:08:29,000
Miss you, my foot.

142
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:30,360
I'm on my way to the office.

143
00:08:37,679 --> 00:08:38,799
I just saw someone

144
00:08:38,799 --> 00:08:39,600
who looked just like you.

145
00:08:40,240 --> 00:08:41,039
Really?

146
00:08:48,120 --> 00:08:49,000
I also saw someone

147
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:49,759
who looked just like you.

148
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:52,240
When we get to the office,

149
00:08:52,480 --> 00:08:54,360
let's discuss the Plot 7 matter

150
00:08:54,399 --> 00:08:55,080
with Chairman Zheng together.

151
00:08:56,159 --> 00:08:56,600
Got it.

152
00:08:56,799 --> 00:08:58,240
I've thought it through from start to finish.

153
00:08:58,519 --> 00:08:59,480
Fang Bing absolutely cannot

154
00:08:59,480 --> 00:09:00,840
get Plot 7 Phase 1 general contracting.

155
00:09:27,159 --> 00:09:28,559
Junjie!

156
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:36,080
Junjie!

157
00:09:36,840 --> 00:09:37,759
Don't scare me, Junjie!

158
00:09:38,879 --> 00:09:39,440
The hospital!

159
00:09:39,879 --> 00:09:40,559
Let's get to the hospital!

160
00:09:48,360 --> 00:09:48,919
Junjie!

161
00:09:49,679 --> 00:09:50,200
Hang in there!

162
00:09:50,639 --> 00:09:51,200
Hang in there!

163
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:52,080
Just hang in there!
